### 1. Create Bid Package
POST http://localhost:8001/bid-packages
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "projectId": "{{project_id}}",
  "title": "Cabinet and Flooring Bid Request",
  "description": "Seeking competitive bids for cabinet installation and flooring",
  "dueDate": "2026-03-15T23:59:59.000Z",
  "attachmentUrls": ["https://storage.googleapis.com/nexus-uploads/plans-123.pdf"],
  "lineItems": [
    {
      "category": "CABINETS",
      "description": "Kitchen base cabinets, white shaker, 36\"Wx24\"Dx34.5\"H",
      "unit": "EA",
      "qty": 12,
      "specHash": "abc123"
    },
    {
      "category": "FLOORING",
      "description": "Luxury vinyl plank, 7\" x 48\", gray oak",
      "unit": "SF",
      "qty": 850
    }
  ]
}

### 2. List Bid Packages
GET http://localhost:8001/bid-packages?projectId={{project_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### 3. Get Bid Package Details
GET http://localhost:8001/bid-packages/{{package_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### 4. Invite Suppliers
POST http://localhost:8001/bid-packages/{{package_id}}/invite
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "suppliers": [
    {
      "supplierName": "ABC Cabinets",
      "contactName": "John Smith",
      "contactEmail": "john@abccabinets.com",
      "contactPhone": "+15551234567"
    },
    {
      "supplierName": "XYZ Flooring",
      "contactName": "Jane Doe",
      "contactEmail": "jane@xyzflooring.com"
    }
  ]
}

### 5. Supplier Portal - Get Bid Package (no auth)
GET http://localhost:8001/supplier-portal/{{access_token}}

### 6. Supplier Portal - Submit Bid
POST http://localhost:8001/supplier-portal/{{access_token}}/bid
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "SUBMITTED",
  "notes": "We can complete this within 2 weeks",
  "lineItems": [
    {
      "bidPackageLineItemId": "{{line_item_1_id}}",
      "unitPrice": 450.00,
      "leadTimeDays": 10
    },
    {
      "bidPackageLineItemId": "{{line_item_2_id}}",
      "unitPrice": 5.25,
      "leadTimeDays": 7,
      "notes": "Premium grade LVP"
    }
  ],
  "subtotal": 9862.50,
  "total": 9862.50
}

### 7. Download CSV Template
GET http://localhost:8001/supplier-portal/{{access_token}}/csv-template

### 8. Compare Bids
GET http://localhost:8001/bid-packages/{{package_id}}/compare
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### 9. Award Bid
POST http://localhost:8001/bid-packages/{{package_id}}/award
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bidId": "{{winning_bid_id}}",
  "notes": "Best value and timeline"
}

### 10. Close Bidding
POST http://localhost:8001/bid-packages/{{package_id}}/close
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}
